THANK YOU @clinique and @katespadeny  THE LOOK:
The look that the Kate Spade team wanted was an incredibly fresh, clean look that focused on a  stained lip and fresh glowing skin and eyes. 
Very minimalist and not fussy or overly made up. 
We wanted to Enhance the natural beauty with soft makeup, warm bright tones on the lips, and sheer nude eyeshadow. This makeup look is as natural as it gets, yet enhances and defines the features in all the right places. PREP-Moisture Surge 100HR moisturizer, FOUNDATION-Even Better Makeup foundation, Even Better Concealer, Stay-Matte Universal Blotting Powder, BROWS-Just Browsing Brow Mousse, CHEEKS-Cheek Pop blush, HIGHLIGHTER-Chubby Stick Highlighter, LIPS-Red Carpet or Red Hot Lipstick, SET-Moisture Surge Face Spray. #cliniquepartner #clinique
Some of my highlights of 2023. Wishing everyone happiness, peace, and prosperity in 2024 Wishing you a joyous New Year!
